text: Anatoly Timofeyev (, 19 October 1887 - 17 August 1985) was a Russian fencer. He competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1985 deaths Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
